  "title": "Hotel Receptionist [Somerset | 6 days | up to $2000] - LCYL",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Hotel Receptionist</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>6 days, 3 rotating shifts – 7am to 3pm, 3pm to 11pm &amp; 11pm to 7am (midnight shift twice a month)</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Salary: $1800-$2000</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Location: Somerset</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Job scope:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Booking reservations for guests, including room rates, room availability, and special requests</li>\n  <li>Perform registration duties for all hotel guests.</li>\n  <li>Reviewing guest check-in information, such as name, address, credit card number, and phone number</li>\n  <li>Assigns appropriate guests rooms based on their preferences.</li>\n  <li>Handles guests requests through incoming calls and performs follows up on guests’ requests.</li>\n  <li>Completing administrative tasks such as filing and photocopying</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Cheong Yeat Long | R25145358</p>\n<p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd | EA 14C7279</p>",
